Entry.JapaneseText: ナニあのデッカイ花!? 気味が悪いヨ!!
Entry.EnglishText: What's up with that giant flower?! It's freaking me out!

Entry.JapaneseText: <Yellow>樹のフォルス<White>の影響で、 植物が異常な成長をしたんだろう。
Entry.EnglishText: These plants must have grown abnormally large due to the influence of the Force of Wood.

Entry.JapaneseText: ねえ、この花、何もしないよネ？
Entry.EnglishText: Hey, that flower isn't going to do anything, right?

Entry.JapaneseText: どうした？ おまえが怖がるとは珍しいな。
Entry.EnglishText: Why are you asking that? It's not like you to be scared.

Entry.JapaneseText: なんかさ、あの花見てると、自分が小さくなった みたいな感じがして、イヤなんだよネ！
Entry.EnglishText: Well, I don't like looking at it because it makes me feel like I've shrunk!
